 *MealMap - Recipe Finder Web Project*:
---
## MealMap – Front-End Web Project

This repository contains our front-end project *MealMap, developed as part of our coursework. It is our first-year mini project, and we have uploaded it here as part of the subject **Source Code Management (SCM)*.

### 📌 Project Overview

*MealMap* is a static website designed to help users search and explore a variety of recipes. It includes multiple pages such as:

- Homepage  
- Search Recipes Page  
- Recipe Details Page  
- Favorites Page  
- About Us Page  
- Review Page  

The project was built using *HTML, **CSS, and **JavaScript*. It is fully responsive and user-friendly, with an intuitive interface and smooth navigation.

### 📂 Repository Contents

This repository includes:

- All HTML files for the individual pages  
- CSS files for styling and layout  
- JavaScript files for handling API calls, user interactions, and dynamic content  
- Image assets and icons used throughout the website  

### 🤝 Team Effort

This website was created by a team of three members as part of our learning experience. All members contributed to different sections of the project, and we used GitHub for collaboration, version control, and managing our source code efficiently.
